title: What my gender transition taught me about womanhood | Paula Stone Williams
itunes:author: Paula Stone Williams
description: After leading a well-established life as a pastor, father and husband, Paula Stone Williams could no longer deny her truth and transitioned. In this conversational and at times humorous reflection, Williams offers her perspective on the everyday experiences lost, gained and once taken for granted in her journey of trans womanhood.
